{
  "id": "adv_card_kan_08_03",
  "title": "kana",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "あ～～、やっと撮影終わった！　kanaにはまだ\n地獄の編集作業が残ってるしさっさと帰ろーっと！",
      "startTime": 6.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "小島さんもお疲れ様でした\n今日は一日、本当にありがとうございました",
      "startTime": 13.6317255534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "叶の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kandad001.m4a",
      "text": "こちらこそお世話になりました。公開楽しみにしてます\n叶は……この後、日本に戻るんだよな？",
      "startTime": 21.6550116856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.0883443832
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "うん、明日出国\nだからお父さんに会えるのは、今日が最後だと思う",
      "startTime": 28.3216783523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "…………じゃあね、お父さん",
      "startTime": 33.4883459091,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.1216792424
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "また記者にゲロったりとか、ヘマやらかしたら\n今度は、今の奥さんと娘さんにチクるからね！",
      "startTime": 39.481906112,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11306.438907,
          "startTime": 50.788345019
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12153.110273800003,
          "startTime": 51.6350163858
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.8883465449
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "叶の父",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kandad002.m4a",
      "text": "あ……ああ、これからは気を付けるよ\n…………それじゃあ……ありがとう、叶",
      "startTime": 47.8883465449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.7550163906
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あの…………kanaさんは、週刊誌はでたらめで\nインタビューで本当のことを話すと言ってましたけど",
      "startTime": 56.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "でも……インタビューは多分、kanaさんの理想で\n本当は、あの記事の方が正しかったんじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 65,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.8749938329
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "……は？\n何よ、kanaが嘘ついてたとでも言いたい訳？",
      "startTime": 70.1083247502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.0083271663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ……ただ一緒に写真も撮ったことがないというのと\n妙に『仲良し』と連呼してたのが引っかかって……",
      "startTime": 78.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "人前では仲が良さそうなフリをしてるkanaさんも\nずっと、側で見てきましたからね",
      "startTime": 85.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.127465852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……こいつも騙せないとか、焼きが回ったな\n事務所の他の奴等には、絶対に言わないでよ",
      "startTime": 94.5607967693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それはもう！！",
      "startTime": 98.4607991854,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.3659694909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "……kanaさぁ。ずっとお父さんに会いたかったの\n一緒に仲良く暮らしたくて、ずっと頑張ってた訳よ",
      "startTime": 105.6326337415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.4993028242
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "ムカつく奴らとグループ組んだり\n零細事務所でドッキリとか温泉営業させられたりさぁ",
      "startTime": 113.3659670749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに頑張ったのに……結局、家族にはなれなかった\nだから今まで頑張ってたのは、ぜーんぶ無駄だったの",
      "startTime": 126.8040260857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.8659694909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "アメリカに来て、お父さんに会うだけは会えたけど\nそれも今、終わっちゃった",
      "startTime": 137.6326337415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.4659694909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "あー、別に慰めたりしなくていいから\n上っ面で言われても、別に嬉しくもなんともないし",
      "startTime": 144.6326337415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.4993028242
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました\nでも、アメリカでの最後の夜なんですよ",
      "startTime": 150,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくなので、どこかに食べに行きませんか\n出来れば、お酒も美味しいお店がいいですよね",
      "startTime": 157.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.6976026772
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.2976002612
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "マジ？　やった、経費で豪遊じゃん\n……やめよ、こういう山田さんみたいな喜び方",
      "startTime": 165.5642669278,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6446.664377800005,
          "startTime": 172.0109313056
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.0309335945
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan013.m4a",
      "text": "今アメリカでバズってて、予約なしでも入れるとこ……\nあ、ここなんかどう？",
      "startTime": 175.0309335945,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ええと……日本円に換算すると……\n……え、円安って辛いですね",
      "startTime": 183.1072122641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――帰国後",
      "startTime": 187.8170366524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 188.9170366524
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan014.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}、見た見た？\n例の週刊誌のクソ記事なんだけどさぁ",
      "startTime": 192.4503675697,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9413.325322199995,
          "startTime": 201.8636928919
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "どうなりました？　こちらで対抗記事は出せても\n結局、向こうの記事の差し止めは出来ませんでしたし",
      "startTime": 199.0503642635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan015.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん。バッチリ炎上中。最初に記事を出すから\nゴシップの価値があるのに、ただの後追いじゃねぇ",
      "startTime": 208.7346051134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "「芸能人でもプライバシー詮索していい訳ないよね」\n「しかも、ほとんどが記者の勘違いじゃん」",
      "startTime": 217.4333302815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-kan016.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、言ってやれ言ってやれ\nゴシップが金になると思ってる老害、まだいるのよね～",
      "startTime": 224.3758977171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_08_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "まぁまぁ、俺達もメディア側の人間ではありますから\n持ちつ持たれつということで、ほどほどに",
